<Legal title="Child Safety Policy" description="7/16's commitment to child safety and protection." locale="en">
  <h1>Child Safety Policy</h1>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 22, 2026</p>

  <p>
    7/16 ("we", "us", or "the service") places child safety as our highest priority. This policy outlines our commitment to protecting minors and preventing child sexual exploitation and abuse.
  </p>

  <h2>Age Restrictions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>This service is <strong>not intended for persons under 13</strong>. Persons under 13 cannot create an account.</li>
    <li>Persons under 16 should obtain parental consent before use.</li>
    <li>If we identify a user under 13, we will promptly delete their account and all associated personal information.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Zero Tolerance for CSAM</h2>
  <p>
    We maintain <strong>zero tolerance</strong> for child sexual abuse material (CSAM).
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Posting, sharing, storing, or distributing CSAM results in immediate permanent suspension.</li>
    <li>When CSAM is detected, we report it to the relevant authorities in accordance with applicable law.</li>
    <li>We retain related data for evidence preservation to the extent required by law.</li>
    <li>Child grooming (befriending a minor for the purpose of sexual exploitation) is likewise prohibited.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Prohibited Content and Conduct</h2>
  <p>The following content and conduct are strictly prohibited and will result in immediate and firm action:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Sexual imagery of minors (whether real or fictional)</li>
    <li>Grooming behavior toward minors</li>
    <li>Sharing, requesting, or promoting content that sexually exploits minors</li>
    <li>Bullying, harassment, or threatening behavior toward minors</li>
    <li>Soliciting inappropriate images or personal information from minors</li>
    <li>Encouraging minors to engage with dangerous substances or harmful activities</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Detection and Moderation</h2>
  <p>We use the following measures to ensure platform safety:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Automated detection technology for photo content</li>
    <li>Human review based on user reports</li>
    <li>Monitoring of suspicious accounts and behavior patterns</li>
    <li>Regular platform audits</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to Report</h2>
  <p>If you encounter content or behavior that threatens child safety, please report it promptly:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>In-app reporting</strong>: Use the "Report" button on the relevant content.</li>
    <li><strong>Email</strong>: Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@stormstory.jp">info@stormstory.jp</a>.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>All reports are reviewed with priority and addressed promptly. Reporter information is protected.</p>

  <h2>Enforcement Actions</h2>
  <p>When a child safety violation is confirmed, we take the following actions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Immediate removal of the content</li>
    <li>Immediate permanent suspension of the account</li>
    <li>Reporting to relevant authorities as required by law</li>
    <li>Consideration of legal action</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Child safety violations result in immediate permanent suspension — not warnings or temporary suspensions.</strong></p>

  <h2>For Parents and Guardians</h2>
  <p>If your child uses this service, please:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Review how the service works (random photo selection, anonymous sharing) with your child.</li>
    <li>Advise your child to be careful about which photos may potentially be shared.</li>
    <li>Create an environment where your child feels comfortable reporting inappropriate content or behavior.</li>
    <li>If you wish to delete your child's account, contact <a href="mailto:info@stormstory.jp">info@stormstory.jp</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Related Policies</h2>
  <p>Please read this policy alongside:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></li>
    <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Policy Changes</h2>
  <p>This policy may be updated as needed. We will notify you of significant changes in advance.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    7/16 Operations<br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:info@stormstory.jp">info@stormstory.jp</a>
  </p>
</Legal>
